32#include "gmp.h"
33#include "gmp-impl.h"
34
35int
36mpq_equal (mpq_srcptr op1, mpq_srcptr op2) __GMP_NOTHROW
37{
38 mp_size_t num1_size, num2_size, den1_size, den2_size, i;
39 mp_srcptr num1_ptr, num2_ptr, den1_ptr, den2_ptr;
40
41 /* need fully canonical for correct results */
42 ASSERT_MPQ_CANONICAL (op1);
43 ASSERT_MPQ_CANONICAL (op2);
44
45 num1_size = SIZ(NUM(op1));
46 num2_size = SIZ(NUM(op2));
47 if (num1_size != num2_size)
48 return 0;
49
50 num1_ptr = PTR(NUM(op1));
51 num2_ptr = PTR(NUM(op2));
52 num1_size = ABS (num1_size);
53 for (i = 0; i < num1_size; i++)
54 if (num1_ptr[i] != num2_ptr[i])
55 return 0;
56
57 den1_size = SIZ(DEN(op1));
58 den2_size = SIZ(DEN(op2));
59 if (den1_size != den2_size)
60 return 0;
61
62 den1_ptr = PTR(DEN(op1));
63 den2_ptr = PTR(DEN(op2));
64 for (i = 0; i < den1_size; i++)
65 if (den1_ptr[i] != den2_ptr[i])
66 return 0;
67
68 return 1;
69}
